desc: 100% remy hand-tied hair extension wefts. We use only the best materials to create our hand-tied hair extensions. Every strand of hair is tied onto the weft by hand. Do not cut the weft, or it will need to be replaced. Hand-tied wefts sit comfortably and invisibly on the clients head by sewing onto beads.
